This is a interactive demonstration of the budget deficit of the states of the United States of America. This has been created by Abhiram, Megala and Nitin at the University of Florida.

Install processing from http://processing.org/download/.
To run this copy all files to the "sketchbook" folder which can be set from the File menu and point to the Ration_alize.pde file from Open in the File menu.
